      <title>随着人民币汇率趋稳，中国人民银行撤回对人民币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/china-s-pboc-dials-back-support-for-yuan-as-currency-steadies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行一年多来首次将人民币每日参考汇率设定得与预期基本一致，这表明央行正在放松对人民币的严格控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/china-s-pboc-dials-back-support-for-yuan-as-currency-steadies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
